# Changelog
All notable changes to this project will be documented in this file.

The format is based on [Keep a Changelog](https://keepachangelog.com/en/1.0.0/),
and this project adheres to [Semantic Versioning](https://semver.org/spec/v2.0.0.html).

## [2.1.0] 2021-07-26
### Changed
 - Made RequireReference have prettier error messages.
 - Made ReferenceResolvers have prettier warning messages;
### Fixed
 - InjectAttribute now works on subfields.
 - PrefabAttribute correctly displays the type of the elements on lists/arrays now.

## [2.0.2] 2021-07-24
### Fixed
 - Cleaned up unnecessary using statements.

## [2.0.1] 2021-07-21
### Fixed
 - Fixed dangling meta file.

## [2.0.0] 2021-07-21
### Added
 - FindGameObjectAttribute searches the scene for a GameObject and assigns it.
 - FindAssetAttribute searches for an asset and assigns it.
 - GetComponentAttribute searches a GameObject for a Component and assigns it.
 - RequireReferenceAttribute forces a reference type field to be assigned before entering Play Mode. 
### Changed
 - Updated minimum Unity version to 2020.3.1f1
 - SceneAttribute shows the filepath to the scene asset instead of just the name.

## [1.1.1] 2021-07-13
### Fixed
 - InjectAttribute now properly handles IList and lets Unity tell you that it doesn't work. 

## [1.1.0] 2021-07-12
### Added
 - PrefabAttribute lets you restrict GameObject and Component fields to accept only prefab assets.
### Changed
 - SceneAttribute now applies to string fields.

## [1.0.2] 2021-07-10
### Fixed
 - InjectAttribute works for lists and arrays now.

## [1.0.1] 2021-07-10
### Added
- Change log.
- Added installation instruction to readme.
